# GitHub Personal Access Token (fine-grained)
# Required for: auto-assigning issues to Copilot cloud agent via GraphQL API
#
# Create at: https://github.com/settings/tokens?type=beta
# Permissions needed:
#   - Read access to metadata
#   - Read and write access to actions, contents, issues, and pull requests
#
# Usage: cp .env.example .env && edit .env with your token
# Load safely: set -a && source .env && set +a
#
# NEVER commit .env — it's in .gitignore
GH_TOKEN=